      out.write("    <p style=\"width:300px\">Ragic gives you the ability to add comments with attachment to every entry created. By commenting on relevant items, we can collaborate and keep track of our discussion. A number is no longer just a number, we know how it got there.</p>\r\n    <img class=\"feature3Img\" src=\"");
